    "passives": {
      "MonarchsWillAElizabethRegular": {
        "id": "MonarchsWillAElizabethRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Monarch's Will",
          "description": "When an ally, including this unit enters the battlefield at the very start of battle or from reinforcements, all allies other than this unit receive a Monarch Token. Monarch Tokens cannot stack. Any attack damage will remove Monarch Tokens.\n\nEach time an ally with a Monarch token is damaged by an enemy attack (even if defeated), this unit will immediately have its TU reduced to 0.\n\nTriggered when this unit enters the battlefield from the allied reinforcements:\n- Ally Spirit is doubled. If Ally Spirit is at 0, gain 1 Spirit instead.\n- Then remove burn (including Mega Healing Burn) from 1 random non-sleeping enemy and grant them Sleep (Forced) for 200TU. This triggers an additional time for each 2 Spirit allies have (up to 5 additional times with 10 Spirit).\n- Then if all enemies are sleeping, all allies have their current TU reduced by 100TU.\n\nWhenever another ally enters the battlefield from reinforcements, the ally team gains 2 Spirit, all allies gain Stealth, and a Stealth Shield.\n\nStealth will overwrite other Status effects on those units. Stealth Shields prevent the next non-stealth status effect a unit would gain while Stealthed from applying. Stealthed units ignore the next enemy attack that would damage more than 1 target. Any damage will remove stealth."
        }
      },
      "HoldGroundAElizabethRegular": {
        "id": "HoldGroundAElizabethRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Long Live The Queen",
          "description": "If this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP. This unit's attacks will not wake sleeping enemies.\n\nThis unit has 75% damage reduction from attacks if allies have 6 or more Spirit.\n\nWhenever this unit damages any number of units with an attack, ally Spirit is doubled at the end of the turn, if ally Spirit is at 0, gain 1 Spirit instead. Then if allies have 10 Spirit, remove burn (including Mega Healing Burn) from 1 random non-sleeping enemy and grant them Sleep (Forced) for 200TU.\n\nWhenever ally Spirit is at 10 at the end of any turn, all allies will be healed for 1000% of this unit's attack and be Purified (negative status effects like sleep, burn or poison are removed). This effect cannot trigger again until 50TU advances."
        }
      },
